Package com.jpn.bowling.components.impl

All specific implementations of bowling or game components interfaces are located here

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BowlingGame
    Main class of the Bowling Game.
    PlayerInfoClearFormatter
    Custom formatter for a clean and more human readable look style instead of requested style with tabs splits
    PlayerInfoRequestedFormatter
    Requested formatter for a tab splits look and feel
    RollsTransformerImpl
    Implementation of RollsTransformer to transform a map of each user with a list of string rolls to a List of PlayerInfo
    RoundClearFormatter
    Implementation of interface RoundInfoFormatter with a human readable style of a Round
    RoundRequestedFormatter
    Implementation of interface RoundInfoFormatter as required by the Java Challenge specification
    RoundsBuilderImpl
    Implementation that defines how scores sent by the users are transformed in Rounds and returns new list of rounds
